{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/rewrite-query-string-to-path-with-htaccess/","webpackCompilationHash":"","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Let's say I have this URL:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">http://example.com/users.php?name=tania</code></pre></div>\n<p>And I want this URL:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">http://example.com/users/tania</code></pre></div>\n<p>I can do so with the following <code class=\"language-text\">.htaccess</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"filename\">.htaccess</div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"apacheconf\"><pre class=\"language-apacheconf\"><code class=\"language-apacheconf\"><span class=\"token directive-inline property\">RewriteEngine</span> On\n<span class=\"token directive-inline property\">RewriteCond</span> <span class=\"token variable\">%{REQUEST_FILENAME}</span> !-f\n<span class=\"token directive-inline property\">RewriteCond</span> <span class=\"token variable\">%{REQUEST_FILENAME}</span> !-d\n<span class=\"token directive-inline property\">RewriteRule</span><span class=\"token regex\"> ^/?users/(.*?)/?$</span> /users.php?name=<span class=\"token variable\">$1</span> <span class=\"token directive-flags keyword\">[L]</span>\n\n<span class=\"token directive-inline property\">RewriteCond</span> <span class=\"token variable\">%{THE_REQUEST}</span> <span class=\"token regex\">^[A-Z]{3,9}\\ /users\\.php\\?name=([^\\&amp;\\ ]+)</span>\n<span class=\"token directive-inline property\">RewriteRule</span><span class=\"token regex\"> ^/?users\\.php$</span> /users/<span class=\"token variable\">%1</span>? [L,R=301]</code></pre></div>\n<p>I can even still GET the URL query.</p>\n<div class=\"filename\">users.php</div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"apacheconf\"><pre class=\"language-apacheconf\"><code class=\"language-apacheconf\">&lt;?php\n\necho <span class=\"token variable\">$_SERVER</span>[<span class=\"token string\">'REQUEST_URI'] . '&lt;br>'</span>;\n\nprint_r(<span class=\"token variable\">$_GET</span>);</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"terminal\"><pre class=\"language-terminal\"><code class=\"language-terminal\">/users/tania\nArray ( [name] =&gt; tania )</code></pre></div>\n<p>Alternatively, you could redirect everything to <code class=\"language-text\">index.php</code> and route it that way.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"apacheconf\"><pre class=\"language-apacheconf\"><code class=\"language-apacheconf\"><span class=\"token directive-inline property\">RewriteEngine</span> On\n<span class=\"token directive-inline property\">RewriteRule</span><span class=\"token regex\"> ^([a-zA-Z0-9]+)$</span> index.php?url=<span class=\"token variable\">$1</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>That's all!</p>","timeToRead":1,"excerpt":"Let's say I have this URL: And I want this URL: I can do so with the following : I can even still GET the URL query. Alternatively, youâ€¦","frontmatter":{"title":"Rewrite Query String to Path with htaccess","thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"fixed":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","width":150,"height":150,"src":"/static/15b1871ea4c811121febad33ed4becb6/4148e/apache.png","srcSet":"/static/15b1871ea4c811121febad33ed4becb6/4148e/apache.png 1x"}}},"slug":"rewrite-query-string-to-path-with-htaccess","date":"2018-06-07T00:00:00.000Z","categories":["Tools"],"tags":["apache","htaccess","rewrite"],"template":"post"},"fields":{"slug":"/rewrite-query-string-to-path-with-htaccess/","date":"2018-06-07T00:00:00.000Z"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/rewrite-query-string-to-path-with-htaccess/"}}}